Pilot 1.2. An Atari port and extension of the Pilot programming language (Taylor-Pilot). 
New in this release are three non-standard Pilot keywords supported by Nevada, Atari and
Apple Pilot: PA (Pause program execution), CH (clear screen), TH (print text without 
linefeed). 
Version 1.2: Y and N supported as standalone commands. CO supported to change
text color.

